lead_paragraph: Antti Niemi made 28 saves, but more important than how many he made was when he made them in the Dallas Stars' 3-2 victory over the Winnipeg Jets on Tuesday night.

headline.print_headline: Niemi Makes 28 Saves, Stars Beat Jets 3-2
